# pgccl

PanGu Collective Communication Library -- Ascend NPU上为PanGu大模型全栈特化的集合通信库。

## Status

Design phase complete. See `docs/plans/2026-03-19-pgccl-design.md`.

## Architecture

```
Rust Plan Compiler (topo/algo/schedule/buffer optimization)
        |
   +----+----+
   |         |
   v         v
torchair    Standalone
graph pass  Executor
   |         |
   v         v
ACL Graph   Fallback
(primary)   (AllToAll/eager)
```

## Key Ideas

- AOT plan compilation: compile entire communication graph, zero runtime decisions
- ACL Graph integration: custom ops captured inside ACL Graph, no graph break
- Ascend hardware exploitation: MTE+AIV+Cube physical separation for true parallelism
- 39 innovation sources: MSCCL++/ACCL+/DeepEP/FlashMoE/ResCCL and more

## Tech Stack

- Rust: Plan Compiler (petgraph, PyO3, rkyv)
- C++20: Custom Ops, AscendC kernels, Standalone Executor
- Python: torchair graph pass, PyO3 bindings
- Build: maturin + corrosion (cargo + cmake)
